Alice. have you ever used drugs before?

253
00:27:14.500 --> 00:27:16.300
When did you first see her?

254
00:27:17.300 --> 00:27:19.470
Five nights ago. in the field.

255
00:27:20.720 --> 00:27:21.640
You were there.

256
00:27:22.850 --> 00:27:24.510
And what does Mary want?

257
00:27:27.060 --> 00:27:28.060
Our faith.

258
00:27:31.190 --> 00:27:34.570
I'm... I'm told we'll have
some privacy in here.

259
00:27:35.440 --> 00:27:36.280
Please.

260
00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:42.030
A little surprised that Father Hagan
missed the press conference.

261
00:27:42.700 --> 00:27:47.410
Yes. well. Father Hagan
is unfortunately not feeling well.

262
00:27:47.950 --> 00:27:49.290
I am sorry to hear that.

263
00:27:49.370 --> 00:27:52.960
I imagine he is pretty excited
about his church becoming a shrine.

264
00:27:53.040 --> 00:27:54.500
Yet to be determined.

265
00:27:56.210 --> 00:27:58.210
Alice is speaking perfectly...

266
00:27:59.170 --> 00:28:01.430
though she has never heard
any form of speech before.

267
00:28:01.510 --> 00:28:02.550
How do you explain that?

268
00:28:02.640 --> 00:28:05.680
There are various degrees
of deafness. Mr. Fenn.

269
00:28:05.760 --> 00:28:08.270
Alice may have been
unconsciously hearing all along.

270
00:28:08.350 --> 00:28:10.600
- Come on.
- Are you Catholic?

271
00:28:10.690 --> 00:28:12.850
I was raised Catholic. Lapsed.

272
00:28:12.940 --> 00:28:15.060
Spiritually and professionally.
it would appear.

273
00:28:15.150 --> 00:28:17.570
My lack of faith could be an advantage.

274
00:28:17.650 --> 00:28:23.200
Having a neutral observer along
to record the process would be healthy.

275
00:28:23.700 --> 00:28:26.450
Now. you may find
someone more devout. but...

276
00:28:26.530 --> 00:28:29.080
But they'd be accused of bias. Yeah.

277
00:28:29.160 --> 00:28:30.500
Give me the exclusive.

278
00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:33.540
Only I talk to Alice.

279
00:28:33.620 --> 00:28:36.630
I promise you I will be fair.

280
00:28:36.710 --> 00:28:40.510
And if. for whatever reason.
any of these miracles turn to be false.

281
00:28:40.590 --> 00:28:42.720
then I personally will take the hit.

282
00:28:42.800 --> 00:28:46.550
Alice certainly seems
more inclined to talk to you.

283
00:28:46.640 --> 00:28:51.140
- Your Grace. this man's reputation is...
- Yes. yes. I know. Vincent.

284
00:28:53.190 --> 00:28:55.690
Everyone deserves a second chance. though.

285
00:28:57.570 --> 00:28:58.860
Even Mr. Fenn here.

286
00:31:20.960 --> 00:31:22.920
I asked if I could join the church choir.

287
00:31:23.790 --> 00:31:26.380
All my life. I've been watching
them sing from the sidelines.

288
00:31:26.460 --> 00:31:28.880
You know the worst part about being deaf?

289
00:31:32.180 --> 00:31:34.930
- You know the worst part about being deaf?
- What's that?

290
00:31:35.010 --> 00:31:36.600
You can't listen to music.

291
00:31:37.730 --> 00:31:38.940
But you can feel it.

292
00:31:39.440 --> 00:31:42.020
You turn the volume way up
and play something really loud.

293
00:31:42.100 --> 00:31:46.530
like the "1812 Overture."
you can feel the vibrations.

294
00:31:47.320 --> 00:31:50.910
Well. it's good to know that you are
just like every other teenager.

295
00:31:50.990 --> 00:31:53.280
So any new favorites?

296
00:31:53.370 --> 00:31:57.410
- I think I might be into country.
- Oh. Alice. keep exploring.

297
00:31:59.410 --> 00:32:01.290
All right. I think I got this all set up.

298
00:32:02.670 --> 00:32:05.800
What do you say we do
a couple real easy questions?

299
00:32:05.880 --> 00:32:07.050
How many are gonna watch?

300
00:32:08.460 --> 00:32:09.470
Well. that is...

301
00:32:09.970 --> 00:32:11.550
That is hard to say. but...

302
00:32:12.510 --> 00:32:13.720
maybe millions.

303
00:32:14.350 --> 00:32:16.470
Mary wants to reach
as many people as possible.

304
00:32:16.560 --> 00:32:19.350
Well. we want to make
Mary happy. don't we?

305
00:32:20.940 --> 00:32:21.810
Okay.

306
00:32:23.980 --> 00:32:25.150
There are...

307
00:32:26.020 --> 00:32:28.900
There are people out there
that don't believe in your miracles.

308
00:32:30.070 --> 00:32:32.280
How would you respond to those folks?

309
00:32:32.950 --> 00:32:34.490
Seeing is believing.

310
00:32:35.490 --> 00:32:37.660
And why do you think Mary chose you?

311
00:32:38.540 --> 00:32:41.000
Because she gives voice to the voiceless.

312
00:32:41.660 --> 00:32:44.210
And I've been silent
for a really long time.

313
00:32:45.420 --> 00:32:46.960
I prayed so hard to her.

314
00:32:47.040 --> 00:32:49.420
<i>I yearned to be healed and she answered.</i>

315
00:32:51.630 --> 00:32:54.970
<i>I opened myself up to Mary
and welcomed her in.</i>

316
00:32:55.640 --> 00:32:59.520
<i>And she heard me. Mr. Fenn.
More than that. she listened.</i>

317
00:33:00.430 --> 00:33:04.440
All my life. people barely
looked at me. like I was invisible.

318
00:33:05.310 --> 00:33:09.070
But now when I walk into the room.
everybody listens.

319
00:33:11.780 --> 00:33:13.780
You understand what that's like.

320
00:33:15.160 --> 00:33:17.700
People used to listen to you.

321
00:33:17.780 --> 00:33:20.490
They used to hang on your every word.

322
00:33:20.580 --> 00:33:23.290
You had so much power. but now it's gone.

323
00:33:24.330 --> 00:33:27.380
- Wait. wait. Alice. how do you...?
- Mary told me.

324
00:33:28.670 --> 00:33:33.090
She looked at you in the field
and saw someone who needed her.

325
00:33:33.170 --> 00:33:36.010
A soul yearning for her touch.

326
00:33:37.050 --> 00:33:40.180
You and the lady want the same thing.
Mr. Fenn.

327
00:33:40.260 --> 00:33:42.430
Spread her word.

328
00:33:43.770 --> 00:33:47.730
Seize this chance.
Spread her word and be rewarded.

329
00:33:47.810 --> 00:33:52.240
Alice. do you have any idea
what I did with my book? I can't...

330
00:33:58.280 --> 00:34:02.450
Alice. I'd like to have a word
with Mr. Fenn in private. please.

331
00:34:12.630 --> 00:34:17.050
- Gyles authorized me to be here.
- You just want to take advantage of her.

332
00:34:17.130 --> 00:34:18.340
And I won't...

333
00:34:26.980 --> 00:34:28.810
I won't let you use her.

334
00:34:34.230 --> 00:34:35.240
Emphysema?

335
00:34:37.110 --> 00:34:39.990
My grandmother had emphysema.

336
00:34:41.280 --> 00:34:43.200
Do you think that's a good idea?

337
00:34:52.840 --> 00:34:56.880
Father Hagan. your niece.
she is a remarkable young woman.

338
00:34:56.970 --> 00:34:59.300
She has a gift.

339
00:34:59.390 --> 00:35:00.600
Now. imagine...

340
00:35:01.890 --> 00:35:03.970
Imagine what the people would think

341
00:35:04.060 --> 00:35:07.480
if they were able to actually see
God's work in action.

342
00:35:08.980 --> 00:35:10.730
Don't talk to me about God.

343
00:35:11.860 --> 00:35:14.480
You'd sell your soul for a story.
and you know it.

344
00:35:14.570 --> 00:35:18.570
I... I guess I don't understand
what is wrong with doing some good

345
00:35:18.650 --> 00:35:23.330
and maybe a few people profiting from it.
like you and your church.

346
00:35:23.410 --> 00:35:24.580
Everybody wins.

347
00:35:26.080 --> 00:35:27.080
Everybody.

348
00:35:28.290 --> 00:35:32.170
The bishop thinks a shrine
would be wonderful for Banfield.

349
00:35:33.710 --> 00:35:34.710
Maybe.

350
00:35:35.250 --> 00:35:37.880
I'm not sure it would be wonderful
for Alice.

351
00:35:40.970 --> 00:35:45.520
When God builds a church.
the devil builds a chapel next door.

352
00:35:49.020 --> 00:35:53.060
I never thought I would hear
a Catholic priest quote Martin Luther.

353
00:35:55.070 --> 00:35:56.070
Mr. Fenn...

354
00:35:57.360 --> 00:36:01.410
we are in an eternal battle
between good and evil.

355
00:36:01.490 --> 00:36:05.160
Wherever God goes. the unholy follows.

356
00:36:05.240 --> 00:36:08.040
The girl who saw
the Virgin Mary at Lourdes...

357
00:36:08.960 --> 00:36:11.540
the world treated her like a freak.

358
00:36:11.620 --> 00:36:16.130
She lived out the rest of her life
locked away in a convent.

359
00:36:16.210 --> 00:36:19.170
In Fátima.
three children saw the Virgin Mary.

360
00:36:19.260 --> 00:36:22.180
Two of them were dead
by the end of the year.

361
00:36:25.810 --> 00:36:27.600
Miracles. Mr. Fenn.

362
00:36:29.680 --> 00:36:30.940
Miracles.

363
00:36:32.730 --> 00:36:34.860
They're strong acts of faith.

364
00:36:35.610 --> 00:36:41.070
And there is nothing that Satan
likes more than to corrupt our faith.

365
00:37:11.890 --> 00:37:16.190
<i>Well. our town was founded in the
early 19th century by Catholic farmers.</i>

366
00:37:16.270 --> 00:37:18.270
<i>The earliest mention
in our records is found</i>

367
00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:21.190
<i>in the county assessor's almanac of 1852.</i>

368
00:37:21.280 --> 00:37:25.490
<i>He refers to it as Banefield.
a place of strange and terrible wonders.</i>

369
00:37:25.570 --> 00:37:27.660
<i>"Wonders"? What does that mean?</i>

370
00:37:27.740 --> 00:37:31.950
<i>Well. it could have been anything.
A two-headed calf. a black goat.</i>

371
00:37:32.040 --> 00:37:34.540
<i>Back then. people saw
the devil behind every tree.</i>

372
00:38:12.160 --> 00:38:15.290
"There are various degrees of deafness.

373
00:38:15.370 --> 00:38:18.880
Alice may have unconsciously
been hearing all along."

374
00:38:18.960 --> 00:38:20.460
Those are your words.

375
00:38:22.960 --> 00:38:25.760
I entered a seminary when I was 19.

376
00:38:27.130 --> 00:38:28.300
The Jesuits.

377
00:38:29.180 --> 00:38:32.430
While still a novice.
I disproved a case of stigmata.

378
00:38:33.270 --> 00:38:35.480
Caught the attention of the Holy See.

379
00:38:37.600 --> 00:38:41.690
I have read several libraries' worth
on the supernatural.

380
00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:46.320
investigated half a dozen cases
of alleged miracles.

381
00:38:47.200 --> 00:38:48.610
Proved them all false.

382
00:38:50.490 --> 00:38:53.120
Oh. you know damn well
I didn't cook this up.

383
00:38:54.160 --> 00:38:56.040
It wouldn't be the first time.

384
00:38:57.080 --> 00:38:59.750
You know. there's this part in the Bible

385
00:38:59.830 --> 00:39:03.090
about forgiving sins.
kind of a major plot point.

386
00:39:04.420 --> 00:39:09.390
If the sinner confesses his sins
and truly repents.

387
00:39:13.850 --> 00:39:15.560
Anything you care to tell me?

388
00:39:16.770 --> 00:39:17.600
No.

389
00:39:29.570 --> 00:39:33.120
That was very good. Alice.
That was... That was excellent.

390
00:39:34.040 --> 00:39:37.000
Next. we should try "Mary..."

391
00:39:37.080 --> 00:39:38.500
"Mary of...

392
00:39:40.250 --> 00:39:41.250
Promi..."

393
00:39:56.430 --> 00:39:58.060
Do you believe in Mary?

394
00:39:59.020 --> 00:40:01.100
- Do you have faith in her?
- I...

395
00:40:02.230 --> 00:40:04.650
Do you pledge to serve her
with all your heart and soul?

396
00:40:04.730 --> 00:40:05.780
Yes.

397
00:40:08.110 --> 00:40:10.240
Yeah. I need an ambulance
at Church of Our Lady.

398
00:40:10.320 --> 00:40:11.990
Father Hagan collapsed.

399
00:40:38.390 --> 00:40:39.430
I can breathe.

400
00:40:42.440 --> 00:40:43.860
I can breathe.

401
00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:51.950
Alice. I can breathe.

402
00:41:05.670 --> 00:41:07.670
Father Hagan's most recent physical.

403
00:41:07.750 --> 00:41:09.880
You'll see the mass
in the left lower lung field.

404
00:41:09.960 --> 00:41:13.470
causing complete collapse
in the lower left lobe.

405
00:41:13.550 --> 00:41:15.680
They gave him six months tops.

406
00:41:18.100 --> 00:41:20.140
Father Hagan's lungs today.

407
00:41:21.230 --> 00:41:24.150
Wait. Are you saying that he's healed?

408
00:41:25.810 --> 00:41:26.860
Apparently so.

409
00:41:27.520 --> 00:41:30.650
What about the kid. Toby Walsh?
Are results in for him?

410
00:41:30.740 --> 00:41:34.990
Boston Children's Hospital diagnosed him
as suffering from muscular dystrophy.

411
00:41:35.070 --> 00:41:36.070
No cure.

412
00:41:36.160 --> 00:41:41.750
While impossible. Toby's afflictions
have completely disappeared.

413
00:41:45.250 --> 00:41:47.340
All right. let me make sure
I got this straight.

414
00:41:47.420 --> 00:41:48.750
that I'm not missing something.

415
00:41:48.840 --> 00:41:52.550
There are three main requirements
to be considered a miracle.

416
00:41:52.630 --> 00:41:57.800
The illness must be incurable.
the cure must be instantaneous.

417
00:41:57.890 --> 00:42:01.310
and the cure must be complete. Correct?

418
00:42:04.350 --> 00:42:05.940
Oh. come on.

419
00:42:07.310 --> 00:42:10.020
This is the real deal. This is genuine.

420
00:42:12.030 --> 00:42:14.400
It certainly appears that way. Mr. Fenn.

421
00:42:14.490 --> 00:42:18.320
The main requirements for a
genuine miracle have been met.

422
00:42:18.410 --> 00:42:21.740
The pope has decreed that the field
where the Virgin Mary appeared

423
00:42:21.830 --> 00:42:23.250
is a holy shrine.

424
00:42:23.330 --> 00:42:25.250
What does Alice mean to you?

425
00:42:25.330 --> 00:42:27.420
Alice is my hero.

426
00:42:27.500 --> 00:42:30.550
I felt invisible. just like she did.

427
00:42:30.630 --> 00:42:33.920
But now seeing what she's become.
she inspires me.

428
00:42:34.010 --> 00:42:35.720
She's holy. You can tell.

429
00:42:35.800 --> 00:42:37.550
She's gonna be bigger than Taylor Swift.

430
00:42:37.640 --> 00:42:40.100
- Nothing ever happens in Banfield.
- No.

431
00:42:40.180 --> 00:42:42.180
This is huge. right?

432
00:42:42.270 --> 00:42:43.640
- Where are you going?
- Anywhere.

433
00:42:43.720 --> 00:42:46.850
- Aren't you happy about the miracles?
- No. sir. I am not.

434
00:42:46.940 --> 00:42:51.020
I like when God stays where he belongs.

435
00:42:51.110 --> 00:42:52.480
Up there.

436
00:42:52.570 --> 00:42:54.940
When he comes down here.
bad things happen.

437
00:42:55.030 --> 00:42:57.530
Floods. plagues of locusts.

438
00:42:57.610 --> 00:43:00.990
The Old Testament God is wrathful.

439
00:43:01.080 --> 00:43:03.240
What if something pisses him off?

440
00:43:03.330 --> 00:43:07.330
<i>The impact to the economy
of Banfield cannot be overstated.</i>

441
00:43:07.420 --> 00:43:10.040
<i>In Europe. the shrines
at Lourdes and Fátima</i>

442
00:43:10.130 --> 00:43:13.210
<i>each attract six million tourists a year.</i>

443
00:43:20.600 --> 00:43:23.600
Monica. I'm surprised
to be hearing from you.

444
00:43:23.680 --> 00:43:26.310
<i>Yeah. well. I talked it over
with management.</i>

445
00:43:26.390 --> 00:43:28.900
We decided ten years was long enough.

446
00:43:28.980 --> 00:43:30.400
You paid your dues.

447
00:43:32.270 --> 00:43:34.730
Well. as tempting as that sounds. I pass.

448
00:43:34.820 --> 00:43:37.400
- What?
- <i>I want a desk. Monica.</i>

449
00:43:37.490 --> 00:43:41.070
Special Sections. Make me an editor.

450
00:43:41.160 --> 00:43:42.700
You're out of your bloody mind.

451
00:43:42.780 --> 00:43:46.160
I am fielding calls from Chicago.
New York. D.C.

452
00:43:46.250 --> 00:43:51.460
Every major Catholic demographic
on this planet is eating this up.

453
00:43:51.540 --> 00:43:53.710
I have exclusive access to Alice Pagett.

454
00:43:53.790 --> 00:43:56.340
You want to talk to Alice.
you have to go through me.

455
00:43:56.420 --> 00:44:01.550
No story without Alice.
which means no story without Gerry Fenn.

456
00:44:04.640 --> 00:44:07.180
- I'll get back to you.
- <i>I'm sure you will.</i>

457
00:44:18.490 --> 00:44:19.450
Who's back?

458
00:44:20.450 --> 00:44:21.740
That guy's back.

459
00:44:23.160 --> 00:44:25.120
I'm gonna need new headshots.

460
00:44:29.870 --> 00:44:31.210
This is my home.

461
00:44:31.830 --> 00:44:33.840
I've never lived anywhere else.

462
00:44:35.460 --> 00:44:38.630
But my uncle felt
I'd be better off at the diocese.

463
00:44:39.880 --> 00:44:41.880
I'm sorry. Alice.

464
00:44:41.970 --> 00:44:43.760
It sucks. I get it.

465
00:44:45.470 --> 00:44:47.140
Where is your uncle. anyway?

466
00:44:47.220 --> 00:44:49.730
He has some work at the church.

467
00:44:50.520 --> 00:44:53.650
I just don't know
what he's gonna do without me.

468
00:44:53.730 --> 00:44:56.020
Like. who's gonna catch him
if he tries to smoke?

469
00:44:58.820 --> 00:45:02.780
I don't know for certain.
but I think he'll be okay. He's a big boy.

470
00:45:04.200 --> 00:45:05.530
Hey...

471
00:45:06.580 --> 00:45:08.540
think of it as a new adventure
you're going on.

472
00:45:08.620 --> 00:45:12.620
And in honor of that.
I made you something.

473
00:45:15.420 --> 00:45:16.750
A mix.

474
00:45:16.840 --> 00:45:20.090
Now. please remember
that I'm an old dude.

475
00:45:20.170 --> 00:45:22.680
So you're gonna have to
put up with some classics.

476
00:45:22.760 --> 00:45:27.100
The Beatles. Zeppelin. The Stones.
Eagles. some Tupac.

477
00:45:27.180 --> 00:45:30.140
But I also tried to figure out
what the kids listen to these days.

478
00:45:30.220 --> 00:45:33.810
So you get some Billie Eilish.
Rufus Wainwright. Smashing Pumpkins.

479
00:45:35.400 --> 00:45:37.190
It's just really important that you know

480
00:45:37.270 --> 00:45:41.280
that there is a whole big world
out there besides country.

481
00:45:42.490 --> 00:45:43.700
Thanks.

482
00:45:46.200 --> 00:45:49.410
You know. you're not as big a jerk
as everybody thinks.

483
00:45:51.200 --> 00:45:53.330
Okay. Thank you.

484
00:45:57.710 --> 00:46:00.590
The lady is happy with you. Mr. Fenn.

485
00:46:01.670 --> 00:46:06.140
All these people praying to her.
believing in her because of you.

486
00:46:10.310 --> 00:46:12.560
Well. you tell the lady she's welcome.

487
00:47:51.990 --> 00:47:54.950
- From the lady.
- The lady?

488
00:48:02.670 --> 00:48:04.170
Different lady.

489
00:48:06.880 --> 00:48:08.970
- Why'd you do it?
- What?

490
00:48:09.550 --> 00:48:11.300
Why'd you fabricate all those stories?

491
00:48:15.060 --> 00:48:16.850
- The truth?
- Yeah.

492
00:48:18.230 --> 00:48:19.350
Fame.

493
00:48:24.230 --> 00:48:27.440
When you are on top of the world
and those lights are on you...

494
00:48:29.070 --> 00:48:30.200
it is...

495
00:48:31.700 --> 00:48:34.740
It's like a drug. and it's intoxicating.

496
00:48:34.830 --> 00:48:37.160
and I got caught up in it...

497
00:48:38.790 --> 00:48:40.370
and I thought I was untouchable.

498
00:48:41.250 --> 00:48:43.000
Pride before the fall.

499
00:48:43.080 --> 00:48:46.090
Does everyone quote the Bible around here?

500
00:48:46.170 --> 00:48:48.550
Banfield's always been a place of faith.

501
00:48:49.300 --> 00:48:50.760
Faith. yeah.

502
00:48:50.840 --> 00:48:52.720
Faith and superstition.

503
00:48:53.550 --> 00:48:58.060
You know. the first day I was here.
my farmer friend and I found a kern doll.

504
00:48:58.140 --> 00:49:01.520
- A kern baby.
- Baby. yeah. Fields are full of them.

505
00:49:01.600 --> 00:49:05.110
Yeah. but according
to my farmer friend. not like this one.

506
00:49:05.190 --> 00:49:07.780
This one was wrapped up in a chain.

507
00:49:07.860 --> 00:49:11.320
and the chain was stamped
with an impossible date.

508
00:49:11.400 --> 00:49:13.780
February 31st.

509
00:49:16.870 --> 00:49:17.700
What?

510
00:49:19.410 --> 00:49:20.410
What?

511
00:49:22.870 --> 00:49:26.670
- Kern babies are good luck. right?
- Yeah.

512
00:49:26.750 --> 00:49:31.800
But they also believe that you could
trap bad things in them. and so...

513
00:49:34.340 --> 00:49:37.260
You know.
they would wrap it up in a chain.

514
00:49:37.350 --> 00:49:42.640
and they would put
an impossible date on that kern baby.

515
00:49:42.730 --> 00:49:44.440
like February 31st.

516
00:49:45.020 --> 00:49:49.780
And they hoped that that would
just keep that spirit trapped forever.

517
00:49:55.110 --> 00:49:57.370
So how is Toby Walsh doing?

518
00:49:57.450 --> 00:50:01.830
Actually. he made the school soccer team.
so it's a real miracle.

519
00:50:02.910 --> 00:50:05.960
Wait a minute. I thought
doctors didn't believe in miracles.

520
00:50:06.040 --> 00:50:08.630
Science and God
are not mutually exclusive.

521
00:50:08.710 --> 00:50:10.210
I could tell you stories.

522
00:50:11.590 --> 00:50:12.420
Fenn?

523
00:50:25.770 --> 00:50:27.150
I've seen this place before.

524
00:50:28.610 --> 00:50:29.980
Pequod Creek?

525
00:50:31.400 --> 00:50:34.990
We used to come here Easter Sunday
for the church picnics

526
00:50:35.070 --> 00:50:36.160
until they sold it off.

527
00:50:37.570 --> 00:50:39.830
- Wait. this was church property?
- Yeah.

528
00:50:39.910 --> 00:50:43.580
Church owned most of Banfield
ever since Our Lady was built.

529
00:50:43.660 --> 00:50:45.290
When? When was that?

530
00:50:46.290 --> 00:50:47.710
Mid-1800s.

531
00:50:47.790 --> 00:50:49.500
1845?

532
00:50:51.300 --> 00:50:52.800
How did you know that?

533
00:51:18.110 --> 00:51:19.120
Fenn?

534
00:51:22.950 --> 00:51:24.000
What's wrong?

535
00:51:29.880 --> 00:51:31.250
I need to speak to Hagan.

536
00:51:31.340 --> 00:51:34.880
Something happened here.
something connected to the church.

537
00:52:05.200 --> 00:52:07.410
Confession is from 7 to 8.

538
00:52:07.500 --> 00:52:09.620
Bless me. Father. for I have sinned.

539
00:52:11.290 --> 00:52:14.920
May the Lord be in your heart
and help you confess your sins.

540
00:52:15.000 --> 00:52:18.880
It's been. oh. some while
since my last confession.

541
00:52:19.800 --> 00:52:20.800
Go on.

542
00:52:20.890 --> 00:52:26.020
I've taken the Lord's name in vain.
been covetous. had impure thoughts...

543
00:52:27.020 --> 00:52:29.390
destroyed many lives.

544
00:52:29.480 --> 00:52:31.650
led many souls into perdition.

545
00:52:32.560 --> 00:52:35.360
And now I've come for you.

546
00:52:35.440 --> 00:52:37.360
Say three Hail Marys and...

547
00:52:38.150 --> 00:52:39.700
I healed you.

548
00:52:40.450 --> 00:52:43.450
Instead of faith.
you repaid me with doubt.

549
00:52:43.530 --> 00:52:45.200
And what did it gain you?

550
00:52:45.790 --> 00:52:50.120
You discovered the truth
at the expense of your life.

551
00:52:50.830 --> 00:52:54.750
And do you actually believe
you can stop me?

552
00:52:55.920 --> 00:52:59.920
Shall I tell you what happened
to those who have tried?

553
00:53:00.010 --> 00:53:03.800
I stripped the flesh from their bones.

554
00:53:04.930 --> 00:53:10.940
I slit their windpipes
and watched the breath slowly leak out.

555
00:53:13.770 --> 00:53:14.940
Satan.

556
00:53:15.020 --> 00:53:17.780
- He gave me the power to perform miracles.
- No!

557
00:53:18.820 --> 00:53:23.360
Pray for your
sweet blessed Mary to save you.

558
00:53:23.450 --> 00:53:25.450
Let's see who's stronger:

559
00:53:25.530 --> 00:53:28.450
her or me.

560
00:54:07.160 --> 00:54:09.450
No. no!

561
00:54:39.400 --> 00:54:40.610
Father Hagan?

562
00:54:53.750 --> 00:54:54.830
Father Hagan?

563
00:55:09.140 --> 00:55:10.260
Father Hagan?

564
00:55:41.040 --> 00:55:42.090
I don't get it.

565
00:55:43.090 --> 00:55:46.840
Why would Hagan kill himself?
He had just been healed.

566
00:55:47.630 --> 00:55:49.890
Who knows what demons plagued him?

567
00:55:51.180 --> 00:55:54.930
This will. of course.
be reported as a tragic accident.

568
00:55:55.770 --> 00:55:57.100
As I'm sure you can appreciate.

569
00:55:57.190 --> 00:56:00.190
suicide is somewhat
frowned upon in our profession.

570
00:56:00.270 --> 00:56:02.650
So I must ask for
your discretion in this matter.

571
00:56:03.820 --> 00:56:06.820
Father Hagan was the shepherd
of this community.

572
00:56:08.110 --> 00:56:11.620
You can appreciate the damage it would do
now that Banfield has been reborn.

573
00:56:14.790 --> 00:56:16.290
Let me ask you something.

574
00:56:18.080 --> 00:56:20.250
When you turn on the news.
what do you see?

575
00:56:20.330 --> 00:56:23.960
War. famine. disease. suffering. hate.

576
00:56:24.710 --> 00:56:26.590
The devil is winning. Mr. Fenn.

577
00:56:27.590 --> 00:56:32.850
Faith is the only thing that stands
between us and perdition.

578
00:56:34.180 --> 00:56:38.350
And this place. this shrine.
will help strengthen our faith...

579
00:56:39.560 --> 00:56:40.810
thanks to you.

580
00:56:42.650 --> 00:56:46.900
None of it would have been
possible without you.

581
00:57:12.340 --> 00:57:14.970
My uncle loved me and cared for me.

582
00:57:15.930 --> 00:57:18.060
He was the only family I had.

583
00:57:24.060 --> 00:57:25.900
You know what. this is...

584
00:57:25.980 --> 00:57:28.780
This is dumb.
We can do this some other time.

585
00:57:30.860 --> 00:57:31.860
No.

586
00:57:33.070 --> 00:57:37.540
Mary relieved his suffering
before calling him to his eternal reward.

587
00:57:38.660 --> 00:57:41.080
She wants us to continue her work.

588
00:57:45.880 --> 00:57:47.130
Okay.

589
00:57:48.460 --> 00:57:49.460
Okay.

590
00:57:54.720 --> 00:57:55.720
You know...

591
00:57:57.680 --> 00:57:59.680
your uncle believed that

592
00:57:59.770 --> 00:58:03.560
wherever God went.
the devil was close behind.

593
00:58:05.650 --> 00:58:07.110
Do you think that...?

594
00:58:09.190 --> 00:58:12.320
Do you think there could be
other forces at play here?

595
00:58:13.110 --> 00:58:15.240
Mary would never let that happen.

596
00:58:18.700 --> 00:58:21.620
Don't doubt her. Mr. Fenn.

597
00:58:22.790 --> 00:58:25.790
She is the Blessed Virgin.
the mother of God.

598
00:58:25.880 --> 00:58:28.920
Her love for us is so deep it burns. She...

599
00:58:33.880 --> 00:58:36.220
Mary is speaking to me right now.

600
00:58:39.760 --> 00:58:43.560
She says. "Doubt weakens faith.

601
00:58:46.770 --> 00:58:48.860
Doubt leads to damnation."

602
01:00:03.720 --> 01:00:06.390
<i>Blurry vision. wobbly knees.</i>

603
01:00:07.140 --> 01:00:09.810
<i>No doctor could find
what was wrong with me.</i>

604
01:00:10.440 --> 01:00:13.690
<i>But one look at Alice and I was cured.</i>

605
01:00:15.280 --> 01:00:17.110
Shut up.

606
01:00:19.570 --> 01:00:23.450
<i>She is the Blessed Virgin.
the mother of God.</i>

607
01:00:23.530 --> 01:00:26.500
<i>Her love for us is so deep it burns. She...</i>

608
01:00:42.970 --> 01:00:44.850
<i>...it burns. She...</i>

609
01:01:17.960 --> 01:01:20.090
<i>"Doubt leads to damnation."</i>

610
01:01:21.550 --> 01:01:22.550
Natalie.

611
01:01:23.340 --> 01:01:24.350
Hey.

612
01:01:24.970 --> 01:01:28.430
I don't understand.
Father Hagan wouldn't have done this.

613
01:01:28.520 --> 01:01:29.810
I don't think he did.

614
01:01:31.100 --> 01:01:33.520
Do you know where
the church records are kept?

615
01:01:34.110 --> 01:01:36.440
Yeah. it's in the back.

616
01:01:36.520 --> 01:01:37.940
I need to see the files.

617
01:01:39.740 --> 01:01:42.240
The funeral is about to start.

618
01:01:44.660 --> 01:01:45.660
Okay.

619
01:02:05.180 --> 01:02:06.800
We gather here today

620
01:02:07.680 --> 01:02:10.810
to pay our respects
to Father William Hagan.

621
01:02:41.260 --> 01:02:44.180
Do you have any idea
what we're looking for down here?

622
01:02:45.470 --> 01:02:48.430
Anything related to 1845.

623
01:02:52.810 --> 01:02:56.020
Behold. I will tell you a mystery.

624
01:02:56.650 --> 01:02:58.940
We shall not all fall asleep.

625
01:03:00.530 --> 01:03:03.360
But we will be changed in an instant.

626
01:03:21.380 --> 01:03:22.300
Natalie.

627
01:03:23.880 --> 01:03:24.880
Look at this.

628
01:03:29.180 --> 01:03:30.350
In Latin.

629
01:03:31.760 --> 01:03:35.430
Oh. God. okay.
Med school had a Latin requirement.

630
01:03:39.730 --> 01:03:42.230
"Testament of Father Prescott."

631
01:03:50.450 --> 01:03:53.080
"Concerning the witch
and the bride of Satan...

632
01:03:54.830 --> 01:03:55.830
Mary Elnor."

633
01:03:57.460 --> 01:03:59.170
For the trumpet will sound.

634
01:03:59.960 --> 01:04:02.380
The dead will be raised.

635
01:04:03.460 --> 01:04:04.460
Incorruptible.

636
01:04:06.590 --> 01:04:08.720
And we shall be changed.

637
01:04:08.800 --> 01:04:11.600
<i>Mary performed miracles.</i>

638
01:04:11.680 --> 01:04:14.100
She could heal the sick. Jesus. this is...

639
01:04:14.180 --> 01:04:16.060
No. no. keep reading.

640
01:04:17.770 --> 01:04:21.110
<i>She claimed the Virgin Mary
was speaking through her.</i>

641
01:04:21.980 --> 01:04:25.320
<i>She would heal you
if you pledged your soul to her.</i>

642
01:04:25.400 --> 01:04:29.200
Anyone who challenged her
met tragic ends.

643
01:04:30.360 --> 01:04:32.950
Finally. the town fought back.

644
01:04:33.030 --> 01:04:35.290
Mary was captured and submerged

645
01:04:35.370 --> 01:04:37.750
- in the icy waters of...
- Pequod Creek.

646
01:04:39.210 --> 01:04:41.830
Mary confessed to serving Satan.

647
01:04:41.920 --> 01:04:46.670
As punishment. a mask
was nailed onto Mary's face...

648
01:04:47.970 --> 01:04:49.880
in the image of the Blessed Virgin.

649
01:04:54.390 --> 01:04:58.140
<i>Mary was hanged by an ancient oak
in the shadow of the church.</i>

650
01:04:59.390 --> 01:05:02.270
- In the name of Christ. our Lord...
- <i>Her body was burned.</i>

651
01:05:02.360 --> 01:05:05.440
<i>her ashes and her soul imprisoned
inside a kern baby.</i>

652
01:05:05.530 --> 01:05:06.820
Contain her!

653
01:05:14.080 --> 01:05:16.620
We command the soul of William Hagan.

654
01:05:16.700 --> 01:05:18.080
<i>Alice.</i>

655
01:05:18.160 --> 01:05:19.790
In the sight of this world...

656
01:05:22.880 --> 01:05:23.880
he is now dead.

657
01:05:30.010 --> 01:05:31.800
Mary has spoken to me.

658
01:05:34.800 --> 01:05:37.850
Tonight is the Feast
of the Immaculate Conception.

659
01:05:39.310 --> 01:05:43.980
To celebrate. Mary wants us
to hold a service at the shrine.

660
01:05:46.980 --> 01:05:51.860
After Mary's death.
her miracles were extinguished.

661
01:05:52.820 --> 01:05:55.910
Those she had healed all relapsed.

662
01:05:56.620 --> 01:05:59.000
Jesus. Father Hagan
must have found this book.

663
01:05:59.080 --> 01:06:02.870
He discovered the truth.
That's why Mary killed him.

664
01:06:02.960 --> 01:06:04.580
Hagan believed that...

665
01:06:05.920 --> 01:06:08.630
wherever God goes. the unholy follows.

666
01:06:09.460 --> 01:06:11.670
<i>These miracles. they are not God.</i>

667
01:06:11.760 --> 01:06:14.550
- Join us at this service.
- <i>It's Mary Elnor...</i>

668
01:06:14.640 --> 01:06:15.510
Pray to Mary.

669
01:06:15.600 --> 01:06:18.310
- <i>posing as the Virgin Mary.</i>
- Open your heart to her.

670
01:06:18.390 --> 01:06:21.310
- <i>Doing the devil's work.</i>
- She brings an urgent message

671
01:06:21.390 --> 01:06:24.850
to share with the entire world.
if you believe in her.

672
01:06:24.940 --> 01:06:26.610
I believe!

673
01:06:26.690 --> 01:06:30.070
I believe! I believe! I believe!

674
01:06:30.150 --> 01:06:34.160
I believe! I believe! I believe!

675
01:06:41.330 --> 01:06:42.460
Natalie.

676
01:06:48.420 --> 01:06:49.420
What?

677
01:07:06.350 --> 01:07:07.360
Fenn?

678
01:07:26.750 --> 01:07:28.880
- Fenn!
- Go!

679
01:07:36.050 --> 01:07:37.260
We need to warn Alice.

680
01:07:38.430 --> 01:07:40.010
Alice. did you have a vision?

681
01:07:40.100 --> 01:07:43.810
Alice. please. What do you
have to say to all the people...?

682
01:07:43.890 --> 01:07:45.940
Not right now.
Please. please. please. Back away.

683
01:07:46.020 --> 01:07:47.900
Alice. a couple more questions.

684
01:07:47.980 --> 01:07:48.980
Not right now.

685
01:07:50.520 --> 01:07:52.900
Alice. will more people be healed?

686
01:07:56.450 --> 01:07:58.070
Why now?

687
01:08:13.000 --> 01:08:15.630
- Now is not a good time. Monica.
- <i>You got a deal.</i>

688
01:08:15.720 --> 01:08:18.840
The Special Section desk is yours.
but I want you in the office today.

689
01:08:18.930 --> 01:08:21.640
I want your interviews with Alice.
and I want access to her.

690
01:08:21.720 --> 01:08:25.020
The story. no. I...
Listen to me. I got it all wrong.

691
01:08:25.100 --> 01:08:27.430
Wait. what is this?
Did you get a better offer?

692
01:08:27.520 --> 01:08:30.480
No. you are not listening.
We need to kill it.

693
01:08:31.100 --> 01:08:32.980
Fenn. you're back.

694
01:08:33.060 --> 01:08:35.440
<i>This is your last chance.
You've got it all.</i>

695
01:08:35.530 --> 01:08:37.950
Look. I know you.
You would sell your soul for a story.

696
01:08:39.200 --> 01:08:40.990
I'm pretty sure I already did.

697
01:08:45.910 --> 01:08:47.000
We gotta hurry.

698
01:08:55.420 --> 01:08:56.960
Alice is in the convent.

699
01:09:04.640 --> 01:09:06.140
Sir. he's in a meeting.

700
01:09:06.220 --> 01:09:07.270
Mr. Fenn.

701
01:09:08.430 --> 01:09:11.850
Before he died.
Father Hagan discovered the truth.

702
01:09:11.940 --> 01:09:15.440
Here. 175 years ago. 1845.

703
01:09:15.520 --> 01:09:17.490
a woman named Mary Elnor

704
01:09:17.570 --> 01:09:20.490
performed exactly
the same healings as Alice.

705
01:09:20.570 --> 01:09:24.620
But the source of her power
wasn't divine. It was satanic.

706
01:09:24.700 --> 01:09:26.740
I know all about this. Mr. Fenn.

707
01:09:27.870 --> 01:09:32.000
As soon as the first miracle was reported.
I had my staff research Banfield.

708
01:09:32.080 --> 01:09:36.590
Mary Elnor's confession is preserved
in the diocese archives.

709
01:09:36.670 --> 01:09:39.130
Why was I not informed about this?

710
01:09:39.220 --> 01:09:40.760
Informed about what?

711
01:09:41.880 --> 01:09:47.430
An ugly occurrence of vigilante justice
that happened almost two centuries ago?

712
01:09:47.520 --> 01:09:48.810
Mary killed him.

713
01:09:48.890 --> 01:09:52.390
Father Hagan committed suicide. Mr. Fenn.

714
01:09:52.480 --> 01:09:53.940
Bullshit.

715
01:09:55.440 --> 01:09:58.110
She will kill anyone
that tries to stop her.

716
01:09:58.190 --> 01:09:59.900
What do you expect me to do?

717
01:10:00.610 --> 01:10:02.070
Call off the service?

718
01:10:02.910 --> 01:10:04.120
What service?

719
01:10:04.870 --> 01:10:06.620
The lady spoke through Alice.

720
01:10:06.700 --> 01:10:11.000
She asked for a service to celebrate
the Feast of the Immaculate Conception.

721
01:10:11.080 --> 01:10:13.670
Absolutely not.
You cannot go through with this.

722
01:10:13.750 --> 01:10:16.670
She will claim the souls
of everyone who believes her.

723
01:10:16.750 --> 01:10:19.880
Why? Why do you do this
to yourself. Mr. Fenn?

724
01:10:21.130 --> 01:10:22.130
You have it all.

725
01:10:23.130 --> 01:10:26.510
Why do you want to blow up
your career all over again?

726
01:10:27.600 --> 01:10:28.970
Because it's the truth.

727
01:10:29.720 --> 01:10:32.890
And make no mistake about it.
I will tell the world.

728
01:10:33.440 --> 01:10:35.270
And who would believe you?

729
01:10:37.520 --> 01:10:40.860
The sisters won't let me in
to see her. Bishop's orders.

730
01:10:40.940 --> 01:10:44.410
Look. I am in the diocese archives.
and I think I found something here.

731
01:10:45.660 --> 01:10:49.120
Listen to this. Mary's final confession.

732
01:10:49.200 --> 01:10:50.910
<i>She was pregnant.</i>

733
01:10:51.000 --> 01:10:53.920
Before she was captured.
Mary gave birth to a son.

734
01:10:54.000 --> 01:10:56.460
And that infant was claimed
by a local landowner.

735
01:10:57.920 --> 01:10:59.250
<i>All right. his name...</i>

736
01:11:00.050 --> 01:11:01.340
Jesus.

737
01:11:01.420 --> 01:11:03.380
His name is Nicholas Pagett.

738
01:11:03.970 --> 01:11:05.050
"Pagett"?

739
01:11:06.090 --> 01:11:07.300
Yeah. Alice...

740
01:11:07.390 --> 01:11:09.260
Alice is Mary's descendant.

741
01:11:09.350 --> 01:11:12.770
Mary made a pact with the devil
for eternal life and power.

742
01:11:20.230 --> 01:11:22.150
"I live through my children."

743
01:11:23.570 --> 01:11:24.740
Alice.

744
01:11:25.530 --> 01:11:27.820
<i>She is gonna live again through Alice.</i>

745
01:11:27.910 --> 01:11:30.370
You're breaking up. Fenn. Hello?

746
01:11:30.450 --> 01:11:32.700
Natalie? Natalie...

747
01:12:59.960 --> 01:13:02.250
Now? Now do you believe me?

748
01:13:03.500 --> 01:13:05.420
Alice is Mary's descendant.

749
01:13:06.170 --> 01:13:10.180
Mary's pact with the devil.
"I will live through my children."

750
01:13:11.220 --> 01:13:13.850
Mary can only live
through her own bloodline.

751
01:13:15.310 --> 01:13:18.100
- Alice is in danger.
- Everyone is in danger.

752
01:13:18.180 --> 01:13:19.600
Tonight's service.

753
01:13:21.520 --> 01:13:25.530
All those people praying to Mary.
feeding her with their faith.

754
01:13:26.730 --> 01:13:29.820
Faith in evil empowers evil.

755
01:13:51.800 --> 01:13:52.760
Gentlemen.

756
01:13:55.010 --> 01:13:58.310
I'd like you
to keep an eye out for this man.

757
01:13:59.310 --> 01:14:00.810
His name's Gerald Fenn.

758
01:14:01.520 --> 01:14:02.770
He's a troublemaker.

759
01:14:03.480 --> 01:14:06.690
We don't want any unnecessary incidents.

760
01:14:06.770 --> 01:14:08.440
- Okay?
- Yes. sir. Understood.

761
01:14:08.530 --> 01:14:09.400
Thank you.

762
01:14:23.460 --> 01:14:26.040
The bishop has Alice sequestered
till after the service.

763
01:14:26.130 --> 01:14:28.960
By then it will be too late.
According to the satanic rites.

764
01:14:29.050 --> 01:14:31.880
Mary will perform a mockery
of the Holy Trinity.

765
01:14:31.970 --> 01:14:35.510
She will call on the faithful
to pledge devotion to her three times.

766
01:14:35.600 --> 01:14:40.850
The third time. she will take their souls
and condemn them to an eternity in hell.

767
01:14:50.990 --> 01:14:53.910
So after the choir finishes the Angelus.

768
01:14:53.990 --> 01:14:57.490
I'll perform the supplications
and the responsorial psalm...

769
01:14:58.240 --> 01:15:00.330
<i>Alice. it's time.</i>

770
01:15:01.290 --> 01:15:02.160
Okay?

771
01:15:03.710 --> 01:15:05.460
Alice. you listening?

772
01:15:06.380 --> 01:15:07.380
Okay.

773
01:15:57.800 --> 01:15:59.220
My queen and my mother.

774
01:15:59.800 --> 01:16:01.850
I give myself entirely to you.

775
01:16:02.720 --> 01:16:04.680
And to show my devotion to you...

776
01:16:05.690 --> 01:16:08.020
I consecrate to you this day

777
01:16:08.100 --> 01:16:10.690
my eyes. my ears.

778
01:16:10.770 --> 01:16:13.280
my mouth. my heart.

779
01:16:13.360 --> 01:16:15.610
my whole being without reserve.

780
01:16:16.200 --> 01:16:19.070
Wherefore. good mother. as I am your own.

781
01:16:19.570 --> 01:16:23.700
keep me and guard me
as your property and possession.

782
01:16:24.500 --> 01:16:25.450
Amen.

783
01:16:25.540 --> 01:16:27.000
Amen.

784
01:16:34.130 --> 01:16:35.260
Let us pray.

785
01:16:38.090 --> 01:16:40.140
This ritual is our last hope.

786
01:16:40.220 --> 01:16:41.890
I will use the kern baby.

787
01:16:41.970 --> 01:16:44.560
imprison her soul
like they did in the past.

788
01:16:44.640 --> 01:16:46.270
It's my fault.

789
01:16:47.060 --> 01:16:49.940
I broke that thing. I released Mary. I...

790
01:16:50.610 --> 01:16:53.730
I was trying to beef up what I thought
was a ridiculous story.

791
01:16:53.820 --> 01:16:57.240
- You never told me that.
- I tried. I wanted to...

792
01:16:57.320 --> 01:17:00.200
God always offers
an opportunity for redemption.

793
01:17:01.530 --> 01:17:05.830
He often chooses a sinner
to serve his divine purpose.

794
01:17:06.450 --> 01:17:08.870
Wait. are you saying that God chose me?

795
01:17:08.960 --> 01:17:12.250
I'm saying our Lord works
in mysterious ways.

796
01:17:13.960 --> 01:17:16.050
Some more mysterious than others.

797
01:17:17.130 --> 01:17:19.430
This calls for the blessing of a bishop.

798
01:17:20.720 --> 01:17:23.800
Or. in a pinch. a monsignor.

799
01:17:25.010 --> 01:17:28.430
Next. the wax must be sealed by holy fire.

800
01:17:29.390 --> 01:17:32.100
This flame signifies
the presence of the living God.

801
01:17:54.840 --> 01:17:56.170
Get back.

802
01:18:03.550 --> 01:18:04.850
No!

803
01:18:06.640 --> 01:18:08.930
Oh. my God! Oh. my God!

804
01:18:24.410 --> 01:18:26.780
We can't stop Mary without Delgarde.

805
01:18:26.870 --> 01:18:29.040
Look at all these people praying to her.

806
01:18:29.120 --> 01:18:31.910
She's feeding off their faith.
growing stronger.

807
01:18:33.330 --> 01:18:34.580
What destroys faith?

808
01:18:36.670 --> 01:18:37.880
Doubt.

809
01:18:37.960 --> 01:18:40.630
Doubt weakens faith.
Doubt leads to damnation.

810
01:18:41.760 --> 01:18:45.890
If we get those people to stop believing
in Mary. we can take away her power.

811
01:18:47.930 --> 01:18:51.520
God. the father of heaven.
have mercy on us.

812
01:18:51.600 --> 01:18:54.690
- Lord. have mercy.
- Lord. have mercy.

813
01:18:54.770 --> 01:18:58.730
God. the son. the redeemer.
have mercy on us.

814
01:18:58.820 --> 01:19:02.030
- Christ. have mercy.
- Christ. have mercy.

815
01:19:02.110 --> 01:19:05.410
God. the holy spirit.
have mercy on us.

816
01:19:05.490 --> 01:19:08.330
- Lord. have mercy.
- Lord. have mercy.

817
01:19:08.410 --> 01:19:10.370
- Amen.
- Amen.

818
01:19:14.040 --> 01:19:15.040
Alice!

819
01:19:16.130 --> 01:19:17.000
Alice!

820
01:19:17.920 --> 01:19:20.050
- Alice!
- Alice. bless us.

821
01:19:20.130 --> 01:19:21.420
Mary is here.

822
01:19:28.180 --> 01:19:31.020
She wants you to pledge your faith to her.

823
01:19:31.100 --> 01:19:33.890
Let her into your hearts. Pray to her.

824
01:19:33.980 --> 01:19:36.440
Pray to our lady of Banfield.

825
01:19:42.190 --> 01:19:43.360
Hail Mary.

826
01:19:44.900 --> 01:19:47.370
You are the undying spirit.

827
01:19:47.450 --> 01:19:50.580
The eternal. the all-powerful.

828
01:19:51.830 --> 01:19:53.700
Hail Mary of Banfield.

829
01:19:54.250 --> 01:19:56.080
Hail Mary of Banfield.

830
01:19:56.170 --> 01:19:58.330
We pledge our hearts to you.

831
01:19:58.420 --> 01:20:00.880
We vow our everlasting devotion.

832
01:20:02.630 --> 01:20:05.380
Our souls are at your mercy.

833
01:20:05.470 --> 01:20:07.260
Hail Mary of Banfield.

834
01:20:07.340 --> 01:20:09.970
Hail Mary of Banfield!

835
01:20:10.050 --> 01:20:12.470
In one voice. we call to you.

836
01:20:12.560 --> 01:20:13.810
Come to us.

837
01:20:13.890 --> 01:20:17.060
Heal our pain. relieve our suffering.

838
01:20:17.140 --> 01:20:18.480
Lead us!

839
01:20:18.560 --> 01:20:20.610
Hail Mary of Banfield!

840
01:20:20.690 --> 01:20:22.860
Hail Mary of Banfield!

841
01:20:22.940 --> 01:20:25.400
Hail Mary of Banfield!

842
01:20:25.490 --> 01:20:26.780
Hail Mary of Banfield!

843
01:20:26.860 --> 01:20:29.410
Hail Mary of Banfield!

844
01:20:29.490 --> 01:20:32.540
<i>Now. Alice. Now is the time.</i>

845
01:20:36.210 --> 01:20:39.500
Do you offer your souls to Mary?

846
01:20:39.580 --> 01:20:41.090
Yes!

847
01:20:42.300 --> 01:20:43.300
It's all a lie.

848
01:20:46.630 --> 01:20:48.720
I faked the miracles.

849
01:20:48.800 --> 01:20:50.600
- Fenn.
- Listen to me.

850
01:20:50.680 --> 01:20:53.060
Do you offer your souls to Mary?

851
01:20:53.140 --> 01:20:54.770
Yes!

852
01:20:55.680 --> 01:20:56.890
Come on.

853
01:20:58.810 --> 01:21:00.560
Alice! Alice!

854
01:21:00.650 --> 01:21:03.520
<i>One more time. Alice.</i>

855
01:21:06.070 --> 01:21:09.990
Do you offer your souls...?

856
01:21:10.070 --> 01:21:11.530
Alice!

857
01:21:11.620 --> 01:21:15.410
Alice! Mary is not who you think she is.

858
01:21:16.120 --> 01:21:17.750
She is deceiving you.

859
01:21:18.460 --> 01:21:19.580
The miracles are false.

860
01:21:23.210 --> 01:21:26.210
There's no Mary.
There never was. It's a lie.

861
01:21:27.630 --> 01:21:28.510
No!

862
01:21:32.390 --> 01:21:33.600
Let him speak.

863
01:21:33.680 --> 01:21:35.560
Let him speak. What are you hiding?

864
01:21:39.600 --> 01:21:40.560
Let him be.

865
01:21:42.650 --> 01:21:44.230
Go ahead. Mr. Fenn.

866
01:21:45.650 --> 01:21:48.650
I fabricated the entire story.
I made it up.

867
01:21:50.240 --> 01:21:51.570
<i>Lies!</i>

868
01:21:53.660 --> 01:21:54.990
Mary healed me.

869
01:21:55.990 --> 01:21:59.500
Alice. I am so sorry.

870
01:22:01.170 --> 01:22:03.420
Your illness. it resolved on its own.

871
01:22:04.000 --> 01:22:05.960
She cured my boy.

872
01:22:08.210 --> 01:22:10.130
It's called the placebo effect.

873
01:22:11.840 --> 01:22:12.890
Your boy...

874
01:22:13.640 --> 01:22:17.100
Your boy believed he could walk.
and he did.

875
01:22:18.680 --> 01:22:20.770
Father Hagan raised you.

876
01:22:21.810 --> 01:22:23.020
He loved you.

877
01:22:23.560 --> 01:22:25.650
He was your family.

878
01:22:25.730 --> 01:22:26.940
She killed him.

879
01:22:27.780 --> 01:22:29.360
<i>I am Mary.</i>

880
01:22:29.440 --> 01:22:32.740
<i>You prayed to me and I listened.</i>

881
01:22:32.820 --> 01:22:34.120
Father Hagan...

882
01:22:36.450 --> 01:22:37.950
he hanged in your church.

883
01:22:39.040 --> 01:22:41.710
You asked me to hush it up.
to cover it up. and I did.

884
01:22:41.790 --> 01:22:44.880
You can't believe this man.
He's a blasphemer.

885
01:22:45.710 --> 01:22:46.590
An atheist.

886
01:22:47.300 --> 01:22:49.630
Mary has been using you.

887
01:22:50.800 --> 01:22:52.010
Trust me.

888
01:22:52.090 --> 01:22:54.300
I need you to trust me.

889
01:22:55.550 --> 01:22:56.680
Fight her!

890
01:22:59.520 --> 01:23:01.140
It was all me.

891
01:23:03.140 --> 01:23:05.400
I made it all up for a story.

892
01:23:10.280 --> 01:23:13.030
Just let me ask you something.

893
01:23:13.110 --> 01:23:16.320
Tell me. what is easier
for you to believe. that...

894
01:23:16.410 --> 01:23:20.910
That an unscrupulous journalist
created a hoax or that...

895
01:23:21.000 --> 01:23:23.000
Or that God himself...

896
01:23:23.920 --> 01:23:26.750
reached down and touched...

897
01:23:28.090 --> 01:23:29.090
Banfield?

898
01:23:38.890 --> 01:23:41.720
Alice. Trust me.

899
01:23:41.810 --> 01:23:45.060
You have to stop these people
from believing in her.

900
01:23:46.100 --> 01:23:47.060
Fight her.

901
01:23:47.150 --> 01:23:50.400
<i>Alice. listen to me.</i>

902
01:23:51.530 --> 01:23:53.530
<i>Finish the prayer.</i>

903
01:23:54.280 --> 01:23:57.820
<i>They must pledge their souls to me.</i>

904
01:23:57.910 --> 01:24:03.250
<i>or you will never speak again.</i>

905
01:24:05.210 --> 01:24:07.380
Mr. Fenn is telling the truth.

906
01:24:07.960 --> 01:24:08.920
What?

907
01:24:14.260 --> 01:24:15.720
Mary isn't real.

908
01:24:17.800 --> 01:24:19.260
Son of a bitch.

909
01:24:19.350 --> 01:24:21.100
Mary is not real!

910
01:24:23.980 --> 01:24:25.560
She lied!

911
01:24:30.770 --> 01:24:33.860
- You should be ashamed of yourself!
- It's all fake!

912
01:25:04.220 --> 01:25:05.810
My legs!

913
01:25:05.890 --> 01:25:07.810
- I can't move my legs!
- Toby!

914
01:25:11.940 --> 01:25:13.520
Move! Get out!

915
01:26:11.370 --> 01:26:12.920
What in God's name?

916
01:26:29.270 --> 01:26:30.480
Christ our Lord.

917
01:27:08.600 --> 01:27:09.470
Fenn!

918
01:27:14.350 --> 01:27:16.310
No!

919
01:27:45.340 --> 01:27:47.550
Alice was your only descendent.

920
01:27:50.470 --> 01:27:52.270
You will never live again.

921
01:28:15.790 --> 01:28:18.250
Alice. Alice.

922
01:28:33.220 --> 01:28:34.680
All right. look.

923
01:28:36.770 --> 01:28:39.520
We both know that
I'm not real good at this.

924
01:28:41.150 --> 01:28:44.570
But Alice. she...

925
01:28:45.900 --> 01:28:48.320
She sacrificed herself for me.

926
01:28:55.620 --> 01:28:57.040
Please. God.

927
01:28:57.750 --> 01:28:58.750
Just...

928
01:28:59.580 --> 01:29:01.170
Just let her live.

929
01:29:02.090 --> 01:29:03.000
Please.

930
01:29:16.430 --> 01:29:18.730
Hey! Hi.

931
01:29:28.950 --> 01:29:30.660
You can't hear me?

932
01:29:34.950 --> 01:29:38.540
I have never said anything
worth hearing my whole life.

933
01:29:43.130 --> 01:29:44.170
Thank you.

934
01:30:54.570 --> 01:30:55.410
He...

935
01:30:56.410 --> 01:30:58.540
He was a good man. Alice.

936
01:30:59.290 --> 01:31:03.290
I have no doubt
that he is watching over you.

937
01:31:06.380 --> 01:31:07.750
How do I know?

938
01:31:09.760 --> 01:31:10.760
Faith.

939
01:31:17.470 --> 01:31:18.720
I've been practicing.

940
01:31:21.810 --> 01:31:24.940
Well. I heard the local paper's hiring.

941
01:31:26.480 --> 01:31:29.030
Pretty sure no one's gonna hire me
to be a journalist.

942
01:31:30.530 --> 01:31:33.150
Well. I didn't say anything
about journalism.

943
01:31:33.240 --> 01:31:37.240
It's more like local zoning laws
and the Farmers' Almanac.

944
01:31:38.870 --> 01:31:40.950
- You can think about it.
- Okay.

945
01:31:43.040 --> 01:31:44.040
Hey.

946
01:31:45.580 --> 01:31:46.710
There was no pulse.

947
01:31:47.710 --> 01:31:50.590
She wasn't breathing. She was gone.

948
01:31:52.970 --> 01:31:54.930
Maybe God was present after all.

